%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lapses%20in%20the%20'Signalling%20Circuit%20Alteration'%20Caused%20the%20Balasore%20Train%20Accident%3A%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F04130454%2FFxnA1qjagAAEj0w-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said%20that%20the%20triple%20train%20accident%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Balasore%20district%20on%20June%202%20was%20a%20result%20of%20lapses%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98signalling%20circuit%20alteration%E2%80%99%2C%20leading%20to%20wrong%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaishnaw%20was%20replying%20to%20questions%20posed%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Mukul%20Wasnik%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20leader%20John%20Brittas%2C%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20the%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20clarify%20whether%20the%20commissioner%20of%20railway%20safety%20(CRS)%20had%20submitted%20its%20report%20regarding%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rear-collision%20was%20due%20to%20the%20lapses%20in%20the%20signalling%20circuit%20alteration%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20North%20Signal%20Goomty%20(of%20the%20station)%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20during%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20signalling%20work%20related%20to%20replacement%20of%20Electric%20Lifting%20Barrier%20for%20level%20crossing%20gate%20no.%2094%20at%20the%20Station.%20These%20lapses%20resulted%20in%20wrong%20signalling%20to%20the%20Train%20No.%2012841%20wherein%20the%20UP%20Home%20Signal%20indicated%20a%20Green%20aspect%20for%20run-through%20movement%20on%20the%20UP%20main%20line%20of%20the%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnaw%20said%20in%20his%20written%20reply%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20crossover%20connecting%20the%20UP%20main%20line%20to%20the%20UP%20loop%20line%20(crossover%2017%20A%2FB)%20was%20set%20to%20the%20UP%20loop%20line%3B%20the%20wrong%20signalling%20resulted%20in%20the%20Train%20No.%2012841%20traversing%20on%20the%20UP%20loop%20line%2C%20and%20eventual%20rear-collision%20with%20the%20Goods%20train%20(No.%20N%2FDDIP)%20standing%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20asked%20the%20government%20about%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20died%20and%20those%20who%20suffered%20injuries%20in%20the%20train%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20railway%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C295%20passengers%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E176%20sustained%20grievous%20injuries%2C%20451%20suffered%20simple%20injuries%20and%20180%20received%20first%20aid%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Ereatment%20and%20left.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcover-your-tracks-the-modi-governments-attitude-after-the-balasore-tragedy%5C%22%3ECover%20Your%20Tracks%3A%20The%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Attitude%20After%20the%20Balasore%20Tragedy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasnik%20further%20asked%20what%20steps%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20to%20prevent%20similar%20accidents%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20minister%20replied%20saying%20that%20instructions%20have%20been%20enforced%20to%20follow%20the%20protocol%20for%20any%20alteration%20works%20involving%20ch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eanges%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eexisting%20system.%20He%20added%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cc%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eoncept%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eof%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERolling%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBlock%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Ewas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Ewherein%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Ework%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eof%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Emaintenance%2Frepair%2Freplacement%20is%20planned%20for%20two%20weeks%20in%20advance%20on%20a%20rolling%20basis%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eexecuted%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20a%20special%20drive%20has%20been%20launched%20to%20ensure%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E(i)%20double%20locking%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Earrangement%20in%20Relay%20Room%2FGoomties%20at%20LC%20gates%2C%20IBH%20and%20auto%20Huts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E(ii)%20Data%20logging%20and%20generation%20of%20SMS%20alert%20for%20opening%2Fclosing%20of%20doors%20of%20these%20relay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Erooms%2FGoomties%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E(iii)%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ES%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eystem%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Edisconnection%20and%20reconnection%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Efor%20S%26amp%3BT%20equipment%20is%20being%20followed%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Es%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Etrictly%20as%20per%20laid%20down%20norms%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Eguidelines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20leader%20M.%20Shanmugam%20asked%20about%20the%20details%20of%20the%20compensation%20paid%20to%20which%20Vaishnaw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Frailway-minister-blames-signalling-lapses-for-odisha-train-accident-295-killed-compensation-paid-101689938684314.html%5C%22%3Ereplied%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CTill%2016%20July%2C%202023%2C%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E29.49%20crores%20has%20been%20paid%20as%20enhanced%20ex-gratia%2C%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E10%20lakh%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20each%20deceased%2C%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E2%20lakh%20each%20to%20the%20grievously%20injured%20and%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E50%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20each%20to%20the%20passengers%20with%20simple%20injury.%20As%20on%2013.07.2023%2C%20258%20claim%20cases%20have%20been%20received%20in%20various%20benches%20of%20the%20Railway%20Claims%20Tribunal%2C%20out%20of%20which%2C%2051%20claims%20cases%20have%20been%20disposed%20off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689949215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flapses-in-the-signalling-circuit-alteration-caused-the-balasore-train-accident-ashwini-vaishnaw%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vaishnaw%20was%20replying%20to%20questions%20posed%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Mukul%20Wasnik%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20leader%20John%20Brittas%2C%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20the%20tragedy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flapses-in-the-signalling-circuit-alteration-caused-the-balasore-train-accident-ashwini-vaishnaw%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interview%20%7C%20'Fully%20Assured%20Caste%20Census%20Demands%20Will%20Be%20Met%20by%20BJP'%3A%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21190141%2FF1O_mLVXgAECncC.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20He%20represents%20the%20Zahoorabad%20assembly%20constituency%20since%202017.%20Though%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20has%20been%20active%20in%20electoral%20politics%20since%202002%2C%20it%20was%20only%20in%202017%2C%20when%20it%20aligned%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20that%20it%20got%20its%20first%20breakthrough%20and%20won%20four%20out%20of%20the%20eight%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Rajbhar%20became%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20March%2019%2C%202017%2C%20in%20the%20Adityanath-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20though%20he%20was%20later%20sacked%20from%20the%20cabinet%20due%20to%20anti%20alliance%20activities.%20For%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20aligned%20with%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20his%20party%20won%20six%20out%20of%20the%2017%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJuly%2016%20saw%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20after%20months%20of%20speculation%20regarding%20his%20future%20plans%20since%20breaking%20up%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20last%20year.%20Rajbhar%20is%20known%20for%20his%20outspoken%20nature%20and%20in%20conversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20covered%20future%20plans%2C%20his%20reasons%20for%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%20after%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20his%20demands%20from%20the%20alliance%20and%20the%20future%20of%20his%20party%20legislator%20Abbas%20Ansari.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEdited%20excerpts%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20want%20to%20know%20why%20you%20change%20parties%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20is%20a%20voice%20that%20constantly%20raises%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20oppressed%2C%20the%20marginalised%2C%20the%20Dalits%2C%20the%20backward%20and%20the%20minority%20communities%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20both%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20in%20the%20assembly.%20SBSP%20%5Bthe%20acronym%20for%20his%20party%5D%20is%20always%20ready%20to%20align%20with%20any%20party%20that%20shares%20the%20goal%20of%20granting%20these%20communities%20their%20rights.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20primary%20objective%20of%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20political%20career%20has%20been%20to%20ensure%20the%20rights%20of%20these%20people%2C%20and%20the%20fight%20will%20continue%20until%20they%20receive%20their%20due%20rights.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20we%20remain%20in%20opposition%20or%20in%20power%2C%20if%20someone%20sees%20our%20struggle%20as%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20switching%2C%E2%80%9D%20that%20genuinely%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20bother%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20changed%20since%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20that%20you%20were%20compelled%20to%20align%20with%20the%20same%20party%2C%20BJP%2C%20which%20you%20used%20to%20criticise%20and%20talked%20of%20removing%20from%20power%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20primary%20priority%20was%20to%20be%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20deny%20that.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20due%20to%20certain%20policies%20of%20the%20BJP%20that%20went%20against%20our%20principles%2C%20we%20were%20seen%20as%20making%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20coming%20into%20power%2C%20and%20we%20aligned%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20been%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20history%20to%20deceive%20and%20exploit%20the%20oppressed%2C%20marginalised%2C%20Dalit%2C%20backward%2C%20and%20minority%20communities%20by%20simply%20taking%20their%20votes%20and%20focusing%20solely%20on%20the%20development%20of%20their%20own%20family%20and%20kin.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocialism%20holds%20no%20significance%20for%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConversely%2C%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20understood%20the%20seriousness%20of%20our%20concerns%2C%20and%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20the%20Dalits%2C%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20and%20the%20minorities%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20were%20willing%20to%20accept%20our%20demands.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20join%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20successful%20leadership%20of%20our%20honourable%20prime%20minister%20%5BNarendra%20Modi%5D%2C%20who%20raised%20the%20flag%20of%20India%20as%20a%20distinct%20entity%20in%20the%20world%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20in%20reaching%20our%20decision%20of%20joining%20the%20NDA.%20This%20fills%20all%20Indians%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20pride.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20numerous%20welfare%20schemes%20implemented%20in%20the%20country%20also%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20our%20decision%20of%20choosing%20the%20NDA%20over%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20led%20to%20your%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20failure%20in%20the%202022%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20SBSP%20formed%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20to%20work%20towards%20the%20welfare%20and%20rights%20of%20the%20oppressed%2C%20marginalised%2C%20Dalit%2C%20backward%2C%20and%20minority%20communities.%20Thanks%20to%20our%20alliance%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20went%20from%20winning%2047%20seats%20to%20111%20seats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20after%20joining%20forces%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20while%20they%20talk%20about%20issues%20concerning%20Dalits%20and%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20they%20deceive%20people%20of%20these%20communities%20entirely.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20giving%20political%20representation%20and%20sharing%20power%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20sidelines%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20SBSP%20faithfully%20followed%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20consistently%20tried%20to%20persuade%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20to%20understand%20the%20right%20perspectives.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20disregarded%20my%20advice%20%E2%80%93%20which%20looked%20at%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20oppressed%20and%20marginalised%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20led%20to%20the%20breakup%20of%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20SBSP.%20This%20incident%20clearly%20highlights%20that%20Samajwadi%20Party%20supremo%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20cannot%20tolerate%20valid%20criticism.%20The%20saying%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emeetha-meetha%20gup-gup%2C%20kadwa-kadwa%20thoo-thoo%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(%E2%80%98when%20it%E2%80%99s%20sweet%2C%20eat%20it%2C%20when%20it%20is%20bitter%2C%20throw%20it)%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0fits%20this%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09-300x144.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09-1024x492.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664435%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20O.P.%20Rajbhar.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40VishvanathYad11%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20also%20talks%20about%20the%20PDA%20%5Ban%20acronym%20for%20%3Cem%3Epichre%3C%2Fem%3E%20(backward)%2C%20Dalit%20and%20%3Cem%3Ealpashankhak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(minority)%5D%2C%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20of%20marginalised%20communities.%20What%20is%20your%20opinion%20on%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20mention%20of%20PDA%20is%20merely%20a%20deceptive%20tactic.%20He%20is%20deceiving%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20attempting%20to%20mislead%20them.%20It%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20deceive%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20especially%20the%20marginalised%20communities.%20If%20anyone%20has%20deceived%20and%20cheated%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20minorities%20the%20most%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20PDA%20slogan%20will%20ultimately%20be%20exposed%20as%20a%20hollow%20promise%2C%20and%20in%20the%20upcoming%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20completely%20reject%20his%20bicycle%20symbol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20had%20taken%20a%20strong%20stand%20on%20caste-based%20Census.%20Will%20your%20stance%20remain%20the%20same%20even%20after%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20been%20advocating%20for%20a%20caste-based%20Census%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajik%20Nyay%20Samiti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Ba%20social%20justice%20committee%5D%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20The%20demand%20for%20free%20and%20uniform%20education%2C%20and%20free%20healthcare%2C%20has%20been%20my%20consistent%20stand%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20The%20stand%20of%20the%20SBSP%20will%20remain%20the%20same%20as%20it%20has%20been%20before.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20now%20that%20we%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20we%20will%20discuss%20these%20issues%20with%20all%20the%20constituent%20and%20allied%20parties%20of%20the%20NDA%20in%20order%20to%20address%20them%20in%20the%20future.%20But%20the%20SBSP%20will%20continue%20to%20push%20for%20the%20caste-based%20Census%20and%20the%20Samiti%2C%20which%20have%20been%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20demands%20from%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20has%20rejoined%20the%20party%20now%20that%20you%20have%20returned%20to%20your%20old%20alliance.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20see%20more%20people%20joining%20soon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20talks%20of%20PDA%C2%A0and%20in%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20BJP%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20lost%20its%20first%20PDA%20wicket.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20way%20the%20SP%20talks%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESavarnas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20gives%20the%20impression%20that%20they%20do%20not%20desire%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20upper%20caste%20community.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20upper%20caste%20people%20within%20the%20SP%20should%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20party.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20many%20leaders%20and%20legislators%20within%20the%20SP%20will%20bid%20farewell%20to%20the%20party%2C%20just%20like%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20you%20discuss%20during%20your%20meeting%20with%20Amit%20Shah%3F%20What%20strategy%20will%20your%20alliance%20adopt%20for%20the%202024%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20open%20and%20frank%20discussions%20with%20the%20honourable%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20There%20was%20agreement%20on%20several%20issues%2C%20and%20there%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20discussions%20and%20consensus%20on%20various%20matters%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20the%20strategy%20for%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20let%20it%20remain%20a%20strategy.%20However%2C%20let%20me%20say%20that%20due%20to%20the%20alliance%20of%20the%20SBSP%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20nothing%20left%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20SBSP-BJP%20will%20secure%20victory%20on%20all%2080%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20under%20the%20successful%20leadership%20of%20the%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20become%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsidering%20that%20you%20have%20emphasised%20on%20social%20justice%20and%20the%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20and%20have%20spoken%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20are%20you%20now%20confident%20that%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20marginalised%20and%20oppressed%20will%20be%20honoured%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20I%20reaffirm%20that%20I%20have%20previously%20stated%20that%20during%20our%20%5Bparty%20national%20chief%20secretary%20Arvind%20Rajbhar%20and%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%5D%20meeting%20with%20the%20honourable%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20were%20discussions%20as%20well%20as%20agreement%20on%20various%20matters.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20ongoing%20fight%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20including%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%2C%20and%20minorities%2C%20will%20continue.%20Whether%20it%20is%20about%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajik%20Nyay%20Samiti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20inclusion%20of%20Bhar-Rajbhar%20caste%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20list%2C%20or%20the%20issue%20of%20caste-based%20Census%2C%20we%20are%20fully%20assured%20that%20our%20demands%20will%20be%20heard%20and%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Pramod%20Tiwari%20has%20said%20that%20no%20one%20can%20guess%20where%20you%20are%20today%20and%20where%20you%20will%20be%20tomorrow.%20How%20would%20you%20respond%20to%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20not%20even%20talk%20about%20Pramod%20Tiwari.%20Coming%20to%20Congress%2C%20the%20party%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20presence%20as%20far%20as%20UP%20is%20concerned.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20national%20party%2C%20has%20become%20insignificant%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20compared%20to%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party.%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20holds%20a%20greater%20number%20of%20MLAs%20than%20Congress.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20Pramod%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20statement%20only%20confirms%20that%20Congress%20has%20completely%20lost%20its%20ground%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20many%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20making%20such%20statements%20due%20to%20their%20own%20perplexity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw-1024x769.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Pramod%20Tiwari.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40pramodtiwari700%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20see%20the%20opposition%20parties%20like%20SP%2C%20BSP%20and%20Congress%20performing%20in%20UP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20been%20deceiving%20and%20exploiting%20the%20backward%2C%20Dalit%2C%20and%20minority%20communities.%20Keeping%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20now%20leaning%20towards%20becoming%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESamaptwadi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EParty%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(extinct%20party).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20has%20completely%20lost%20its%20ground%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20has%20no%20support%20left.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20has%20its%20vote%20bank%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20stand%20against%20the%20NDA%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20it%20is%20thoroughly%20entrenched%20in%20corruption%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20significant%20distress%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20Many%20of%20their%20prominent%20leaders%20and%20ministers%20have%20even%20been%20sent%20to%20jail.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20SBSP%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20the%20survival%20of%20these%20parties%20almost%20impossible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20the%20main%20issues%20on%20which%20you%20have%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%20are%20not%20fulfilled%2C%20shall%20we%20once%20again%20see%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%20leaving%20the%20NDA%20alliance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20several%20issues%20on%20which%20discussions%20have%20taken%20place%20and%20agreements%20have%20been%20reached.%20Even%20in%20the%20future%2C%20there%20will%20be%20discussions%20on%20many%20such%20issues%2C%20and%20consensus%20will%20be%20reached%20on%20them.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20there%20is%20consensus%20on%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20leaving%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20alliance.%20Those%20who%20are%20making%20such%20statements%20are%20completely%20unsettled%20by%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20They%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20their%20own%20defeat%20even%20before%20it%20happens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20seats%20do%20you%20expect%20your%20party%20to%20get%20in%20the%20coalition%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20there%20is%20a%20consensus%20on%20several%20key%20issues%20and%20agreements%20have%20been%20reached%2C%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20becomes%20less%20significant.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20in%20the%20alliance%20with%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20carries%20its%20own%20importance.%20The%20allocation%20of%20seats%20is%20a%20mere%20formality%2C%20and%20the%20final%20decision%20regarding%20seats%20will%20be%20made%20through%20discussions%20between%20our%20leadership%20and%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20all%20the%20leaders%20of%20your%20party%20also%20be%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%3F%20Including%20Abbas%20Ansari%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20no%20specific%20individual%20from%20our%20party%20has%20joined%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20The%20coalition%20formed%20is%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20Abbas%20Ansari%2C%20he%20was%20part%20of%20the%20coalition%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20during%20the%202022%20state%20assembly%20elections.%20Under%20that%20coalition%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20fielded%2012%20candidates%20on%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party.%20Upholding%20the%20principles%20of%20coalition%20unity%2C%20we%20supported%20those%20candidates%20under%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20symbol.%20Abbas%20Ansari%20is%20one%20of%20those%20candidates.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20Abbas%20Ansari%20has%20to%20decide%20whether%20he%20will%20remain%20with%20us%20or%20decides%20to%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20we%20now%20consider%20this%20as%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20final%20decision%3F%20Will%20SBSP%20now%20continue%20to%20be%20with%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20we%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA.%20It%20has%20been%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20that%20whenever%20we%20have%20been%20in%20an%20alliance%2C%20we%20have%20remained%20steadfast%20and%20committed%20to%20it%20with%20full%20strength%20and%20honesty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20you%20like%20to%20share%20your%20hopes%20regarding%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20alliance%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20ensured%20that%20there%20is%20no%20opposition%20left%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20the%20upcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20all%20the%20NDA%20will%20work%20together%20to%20win%20all%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20With%20even%20more%20seats%20than%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20we%20will%20secure%20a%20massive%20majority%20and%20ensure%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20government%20and%20contribute%20in%20putting%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20office%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689946421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21190141%2FF1O_mLVXgAECncC.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-fully-assured-caste-census-demands-will-be-met-by-bjp-o-p-rajbhar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22July%2016%20saw%20Rajbhar's%20return%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20Angry%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20veteran%20politician%20says%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20marginalised%20within%20the%20NDA%20fold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-fully-assured-caste-census-demands-will-be-met-by-bjp-o-p-rajbhar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Andhra%20Govt%20Initiates%20Legal%20Action%20Against%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20Over%20Human%20Trafficking%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F31161225%2FPawan_Kalyan.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20booked%20actor-turned-politician%20and%20Janasena%20chief%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan%2C%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmaking%20objectionable%20comments%20on%20the%20ward%20and%20village%20volunteers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20July%2020%2C%20the%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20government%20issued%20GO-Rt%2016%20granting%20permission%20to%20authorities%20concerned%20for%20the%20prosecution%20of%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20under%20Section%20199%20(4)(b)%20of%20the%20code%20of%20criminal%20procedure%2C%201973.%20Going%20forward%2C%20a%20public%20prosecutor%20will%20file%20a%20complaint%20at%20a%20competent%20court%20against%20Kalyan%20for%20making%20allegedly%20baseless%20allegations%20against%20village%C2%A0and%20ward%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Eluru%20on%20July%209%2C%20Kalyan%20had%20said%20that%20the%20data%20collected%20by%20village%20and%20ward%20volunteers%20is%20being%20used%20by%20anti-social%20elements%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctrap%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Ckidnap%E2%80%9D%20women%20in%20the%20state%2C%20linking%20it%20to%20alleged%20human%20trafficking%20from%20the%20state.%20He%20had%20said%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Police%20could%20trace%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20only%2014%2C000%20women%20out%20of%2029%2C000%20women%20who%20had%20gone%20missing%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20clue%20yet%20on%20others.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20had%20said%20that%20he%20received%20the%20information%20from%20central%20probe%20agencies%2C%20and%20was%20specifically%20asked%20by%20them%20to%20share%20it%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20over%20office%20in%20May%202019%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20government%20set%20up%20a%20new%20system%20which%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98village%20volunteers%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98village%20secretariats%E2%80%99.%20The%20government%20recruited%20unemployed%20youth%20to%20man%20the%20system%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20government%20schemes%20reach%20every%20home.%20However%2C%20the%20system%20has%20drawn%20criticism%2C%20for%20long%2C%20from%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20have%20been%20accusing%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20of%20recruiting%20its%20party%20workers%20as%20village%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalyan%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20of%20the%20system%2C%20however%2C%20has%20drawn%20attention%20to%20the%20alleged%20criminal%20activities%20by%20village%20volunteers.%20Several%20village%20volunteers%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20Janasena%20chief%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20making%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csensational%E2%80%9D%20allegations%20for%20deriving%20political%20mileage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20order%20against%20Kalyan%20said%20that%20to%20suggest%20that%2029%2C000%20women%20disappeared%20because%20of%20the%20volunteers%20and%20accusing%20them%20of%20being%20a%20part%20of%20data%20theft%20is%20highly%20objectionable.%20He%20suppressed%20facts%20and%20objectives%20of%20the%20volunteer%20system%20and%20made%20defamatory%20statements%2C%20which%20caused%20substantial%20damage%20to%20the%20reputation%20of%20volunteers%20as%20well%20as%20the%20state%20government%2C%20the%20GO%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalyan%20reacted%20sharply%20to%20the%20orders%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20prepared%20to%20go%20to%20jail%20and%20be%20beaten%20up.%20I%20know%20the%20risk%20in%20casting%20doubts%20on%20the%20very%20purpose%20of%20the%20system%20of%20volunteers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fap-government-issues-go-16-for-initiating-legal-action-against-jsp-chief-pawan-kalyan-for-his-remarks-on-village-ward-volunteers%2Farticle67101968.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20the%20government%20will%20haul%20me%20up%20for%20making%20the%20remarks%20on%20the%20volunteers.%20Chief%20Minister%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20should%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20be%20wary%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20and%20courts%20are%20watching%20how%20murderers%20are%20being%20protected%20under%20his%20watch.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Kalyan%E2%80%99s%20Janasena%20is%20not%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20has%20lately%20sharpened%20its%20attack%20against%20Kalyan.%20There%20are%20indications%20that%20the%20major%20opposition%20party%2C%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%2C%20may%20tie%20up%20with%20Janasena%20in%20launching%20a%20joint%20fight%20against%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20which%20could%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20at%20least%20arithmetically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%20chief%2C%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20government%20for%20issuing%20orders%20to%20prosecute%20Kalyan.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20case%20was%20to%20be%20booked%2C%20it%20should%20be%20first%20done%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20Y.%20S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20for%20misusing%20the%20government%20institutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Ftdp-president-chandrababu-naidu-condemns-booking-of-case-against-jana-sena-chief-pawan-kalyan%2Farticle67105294.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20both%20TDP%20and%20Janasena%20have%20been%20sending%20signals%20to%20become%20part%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20alliance.%20Although%20Janasena%20was%20invited%20to%20the%20recent%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20same%20was%20not%20extended%20to%20TDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689945054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F31161225%2FPawan_Kalyan.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fandhra-govt-initiates-legal-action-against-pawan-kalyan-over-human-trafficking-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Janasena%20chief%20alleged%20that%20the%20'village%20volunteers'%20of%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20government%20are%20resorting%20to%20data%20theft%20of%20women%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20is%20being%20used%20in%20human%20trafficking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fandhra-govt-initiates-legal-action-against-pawan-kalyan-over-human-trafficking-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Project%20Cheetah%3A%20Radio%20Collars%20Removed%20from%202%20More%3B%20'Don%E2%80%99t%20Talk%20to%20Media%2C'%20Officials%20Told%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F20163920%2F2022_9img17_Sep_2022_PTI09_17_2022_000044B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20where%20African%20cheetahs%20have%20been%20released%20into%20the%20wild%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20two%20more%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%20Aasha%20and%20Dheera%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20enclosure%20for%20health%20examinations%20and%20their%20radio%20collars%20taken%20off.%20This%20brings%20the%20number%20of%20cheetahs%20whose%20radio%20collars%20have%20been%20removed%20to%20five%2C%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20last%20week%20that%20experts%20have%20said%20were%20caused%20by%20radio%20collar%20infections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20there%20is%20also%20a%20gag%20order%20of%20sorts%20now%20on%20officials%20and%20experts%20involved%20in%20the%20Project%20that%20prevents%20them%20from%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%20about%20the%20current%20status%20of%20the%20project%20and%20its%20cheetahs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Traumatic%20shock%E2%80%99%20killed%20three%20cheetahs%20so%20far%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20July%2020.%20The%20response%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20indicate%20what%20caused%20the%20traumatic%20shock%20that%20led%20to%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20death.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Traumatic%20shock%E2%80%99%20killed%20three%20cheetahs%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%20cheetahs%20named%20Tejas%2C%20Suraj%20and%20Daksha%20died%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20Choubey%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20at%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20July%2020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20said%20this%20in%20response%20to%20a%20query%20posed%20by%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20Vivek%20Tankha%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20asking%20whether%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20has%20investigated%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20and%20what%20steps%20were%20being%20taken%20to%20mitigate%20this%20and%20sustain%20their%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProject%20Cheetah%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20intercontinental%20translocation%20programme%20that%20aims%20to%20introduce%20the%20African%20cheetah%20in%20some%20Indian%20grasslands%20%E2%80%93%20has%20witnessed%20the%20deaths%20of%20five%20adult%20cheetahs%20so%20far%2C%20of%20the%2020%20that%20arrived%20in%20Kuno%20from%20Namibia%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%20September%20last%20year%20and%20March%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20these%2C%20the%20last%20two%20deaths%20%E2%80%93%20of%20males%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20%E2%80%93%20have%20courted%20controversy.%20Experts%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20deaths%20were%20caused%20by%20septicaemia%2C%20an%20infection%20of%20the%20bloodstream%2C%20brought%20on%20by%20the%20combined%20effects%20of%20abrasion%20of%20radio%20collars%20fitted%20on%20their%20necks%20and%20moisture%20accumulated%20under%20the%20collars%2C%20which%20progressed%20to%20dermatitis%2C%20sepsis%20and%20ultimately%2C%20death.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20implements%20and%20oversees%20Project%20Cheetah%20%E2%80%93%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fauthorities-say-recent-cheetah-deaths-due-to-natural-causes-mp-chief-wildlife-warden-transferred%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einsisted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20all%20cheetah%20deaths%20have%20been%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%20Choubey%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20Tankha%E2%80%99s%20questions%20detailed%20the%20reasons%20of%20deaths%20of%20all%20five%20cheetahs%20that%20have%20died%20so%20far%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah.%20Cheetahs%20Sasha%20(the%20first%20cheetah%20to%20die%2C%20on%20March%2027%20this%20year)%20and%20Uday%20died%20of%20chronic%20renal%20and%20cardiopulmonary%20failure%20respectively%2C%20the%20reply%20said.%20The%20deaths%20of%20three%20of%20the%20cubs%20born%20to%20cheetah%20Jwala%20were%20due%20to%20heat%20stroke.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deaths%20of%20three%20adults%20%E2%80%93%20Tejas%2C%20Suraj%20and%20Daksha%20%E2%80%93%20were%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctraumatic%20shock%E2%80%9D%2C%20Choubey%E2%80%99s%20reply%20said.%20However%2C%20the%20response%20by%20the%20minister%20does%20not%20include%20what%20caused%20the%20traumatic%20shock%20to%20the%20three%20cheetahs%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20Daksha%20is%20purported%20to%20have%20died%20due%20to%20a%20violent%20mating%20event%20on%20May%209.%20After%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20last%20week%2C%20and%20experts%20attributing%20this%20to%20the%20radio%20collars%20that%20the%20animals%20have%20been%20fitted%20with%2C%20authorities%20have%20been%20conducting%20health%20examinations%20of%20the%20remaining%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%20including%20those%20free-ranging%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERadio%20collars%20of%20two%20more%20cheetahs%20removed%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20a%20press%20note%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20forest%20department%20on%20July%2020%2C%20two%20more%20free-ranging%20cheetahs%20%E2%80%93%20Aasha%20and%20Dheera%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20their%20enclosures%20for%20health%20checks.%20Their%20radio%20collars%20have%20also%20been%20removed%2C%20and%20the%20animals%20will%20be%20kept%20in%20their%20enclosures%20for%20further%20health%20inspections.%20The%20animals%20are%20currently%20healthy%2C%20as%20per%20the%20press%20note.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAasha%20and%20Dheera%20join%20the%20other%20previously%20free-ranging%20cheetahs%20Pavan%2C%20Gaurav%20and%20Shaurya%20in%20captivity%3B%20the%20latter%20three%20were%20brought%20back%20to%20their%20enclosures%20over%20the%20weekend%20and%20health%20checks%20done.%20In%20total%2C%20five%20cheetahs%20have%20now%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20enclosure%20from%20their%20free-ranging%20conditions%20in%20Kuno.%20And%20radio%20collars%20on%20all%20five%20have%20been%20removed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20talk%20to%20media%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20from%20sources%20that%20officials%20as%20well%20as%20experts%20providing%20technical%20support%20and%20involved%20in%20Project%20Cheetah%20are%20under%20%E2%80%9Cstrict%20instructions%E2%80%9D%20to%20not%20speak%20to%20the%20press%20about%20any%20aspects%20pertaining%20to%20the%20cheetahs%20or%20the%20project.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%20or%20the%20member%20secretary%20of%20the%20NTCA%20can%20communicate%20to%20the%20media%2C%20and%20that%20too%20via%20a%20written%20press%20note%2C%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689944656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F20163920%2F2022_9img17_Sep_2022_PTI09_17_2022_000044B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-cheetah-media-gag-order%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20said%20in%20parliament%20that%20%E2%80%98traumatic%20shock%E2%80%99%20killed%20the%20cheetahs%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%2C%20who%20died%20recently%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20female%20Daksha%20in%20May.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-cheetah-media-gag-order%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Video%3A%20What%20Connects%203%20Kuki%20Women%20Stripped%2C%20Paraded%20Naked%20to%20Manorama%20and%20Bilkis%20Bano%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21180403%2Fimage-1162.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20nights%20ago%2C%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98no%20connectivity%E2%80%99%20zone%20in%20a%20remote%20part%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20what%20my%20phone%20feed%20flashed%20was%20a%20video%20already%20viral%20%E2%80%93%20two%20terrified%20Kuki%20women%2C%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20abused%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20Meitei%20men%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20WhatsApp%2C%20I%20found%20several%20groups%20from%20across%20the%20Northeast%20where%20the%20video%20was%20already%20the%20major%20point%20of%20discussion.%20What%20stood%20out%20as%20a%20common%20strain%20in%20all%20of%20those%20chats%20was%3A%20%3Cem%3EHow%20could%20our%20men%20do%20this%20to%20our%20women%3F%20Is%20this%20our%20Northeast%3F%20Are%20these%20our%20men%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Instagram%2C%20a%20prominent%20Assamese%20who%20organises%20a%20Northeast%20festival%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20elsewhere%20commented%3A%20%E2%80%9CDisgusting.%20Manipur%2C%20you%20have%20let%20all%20of%20us%20(read%20Northeasterner)%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Twitter%2C%20the%20first%20post%20that%20popped%20up%20on%20my%20screen%20was%20from%20a%20young%20politician%20and%20former%20student%20leader%20of%20Assam%2C%20Luringjyoti%20Gogoi.%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20used%20to%20take%20pride%20in%20the%20level%20of%20respect%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20Yesterday%E2%80%99s%20video%20from%20Manipur%20has%20shattered%20and%20devastated%20me%E2%80%A6Are%20we%20allowing%20ourselves%20to%20become%20animals%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20million%20thoughts%20swirled%20in%20my%20head%20even%20as%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20swallow%20the%20harrowing%20details%20now%20overtaking%20my%20timeline.%20So%20much%20was%20tumbling%20out%20of%20Manipur%20on%20my%20digital%20feed%2C%20from%20a%20state%20badly%20battered%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20two%20communities%20for%20nearly%20three%20months%20now%20%E2%80%93%20completely%20abandoned%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20double%20engine%2C%20having%20just%20succeeded%20in%20grinding%20down%20and%20trivialising%20the%20horror%2C%20has%20no%20route%20map%20for%20redress%20or%20peace.%20I%20particularly%20recalled%20writing%20down%20in%20my%20notepad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-imphal-violence-daughters-killed%5C%22%3Ewhat%20two%20distressed%20fathers%20from%20a%20Kuki%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20had%20told%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20telephone%20on%20May%2029.%20Their%20daughters%20were%20killed%20at%20their%20place%20of%20work%20in%20Imphal%20on%20May%205.%20Their%20fathers%20said%20they%20suspected%20their%20girls%20were%20raped%20before%20they%20were%20murdered%20but%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20confirm%20it%2C%20since%20they%20feared%20travelling%20to%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20Imphal%20to%20claim%20the%20bodies%20kept%20at%20the%20morgue%20of%20a%20government-run%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20did%20such%20horror%20unfold%20before%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20May%204%20video%20also%20made%20me%20wonder%2C%20when%20was%20it%20last%20that%20such%20a%20horrifying%20episode%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20women%20had%20been%20documented%20in%20my%20region%20during%20an%20ethnic%20fight%20between%20two%20communities%3F%20Gradually%2C%20a%20canvas%20emerged%3B%20things%20fell%20in%20place%2C%20aided%20principally%20by%20some%20key%20words%20that%20had%20appeared%20in%20those%20shocked%20reactions%20I%20had%20soaked%20in%20on%20social%20media%20from%20across%20the%20Northeast%20on%20the%20brutality%20and%20shamelessness%20of%20a%20bunch%20of%20men%20from%20within%20the%20region.%20Those%20key%20words%20were%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Eus%2C%20our%2C%20we.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20conflict%20is%20not%20new%20to%20Manipur%20and%20to%20the%20Northeast%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20tribe%2Fcommunity%20burning%20down%20another%E2%80%99s%20property%20is%20not%20new%20either%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20it%E2%80%99s%20seen%20as%20a%20pattern.%20Killings%20too%20are%20not%20new%2C%20unfortunately%3B%20a%20disturbing%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20also%20reckoned%20that%20cases%20of%20rape%20and%20sexual%20assault%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20long-drawn%20out%20militancy-affected%20Northeast%20%E2%80%93%20have%20more%20often%20than%20not%20been%20examples%20of%20our%20women%20violated%20by%20%3Cem%3Etheir%20%3C%2Fem%3Emen.%20%3Cem%3ETheir%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20here%2C%20means%20the%20face%20of%20the%20state%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%93%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20men%20who%20typically%20belonged%20to%20the%20mainland%2C%20accused%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20women%20from%20the%20region%20often%20under%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special)%20Powers%20Act%20(AFSPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20knock%20at%20the%20door%20in%202000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20mind%20sharply%20recalled%20the%20night%20of%20June%2013%2C%202000.%20A%20knock%20at%20the%20door%20of%20Naruttom%20Haloi%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Nalbari%20district%2C%20preceded%20a%20harrowing%20time%20for%20his%20family.%20A%20group%20of%20Army%20jawans%20had%20surrounded%20their%20modest%20house.%20No%20sooner%20did%20Haloi%20open%20the%20door%2C%20heavy%20boots%20barged%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaloi%20lived%20with%20two%20wives.%20The%20first%20wife%20and%20he%20were%20badly%20beaten%2C%20and%20then%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20jawans%2C%20thereafter%2C%20dragged%20a%20frightened%20second%20wife%20from%20under%20a%20bed%20and%20allegedly%20gangraped%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaloi%20and%20his%20first%20wife%20screamed%20for%20help%3B%20villagers%20came%3B%20the%20jawans%20fled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Assam-based%20Manav%20Adhikar%20Sangram%20Samiti%20(MASS)%2C%20which%20later%20documented%20the%20case%20based%20on%20the%20victim%20and%20witness%20testimonials%2C%20Haloi%20took%20his%20second%20wife%20to%20the%20nearest%20army%20camp%20the%20next%20morning%20to%20complain%20to%20the%20officer%20in%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Haloi%20family%E2%80%99s%20testimony%20to%20MASS%2C%20handed%20them%20Rs%20200%20and%20five%20kilograms%20of%20rice.%20In%20a%20state%20with%20AFSPA%20at%20play%2C%20that%20generosity%20of%20the%20man%20in%20uniform%20came%20laced%20with%20sharp%20advice%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20speak%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20anyone.%20The%20scared%20duo%20trod%20back%20home%2C%20and%20never%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeinous%20crimes%20like%20this%20one%20that%20took%20place%2023%20years%20ago%20in%20Assam%2C%20and%20the%20one%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kangpokpi%20district%20recorded%20on%20May%204%2C%20have%20a%20parallel%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20never%20be%20documented%20fully%20without%20taking%20into%20cognisance%20the%20patriarchal%20pull%20and%20push%20of%20%3Cem%3Eour%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20right%20over%20their%20bodies%20against%20their%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20humid%20day%20in%20Nalbari%2C%20the%20army%20officer%20could%20most%20likely%20offer%20that%20appalling%20advice%20to%20the%20hapless%20rape%20survivor%20seeking%20justice%20from%20him%20only%20because%20she%20was%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20woman.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20forget%20a%20fundamental%20thought%20that%20must%20have%20driven%20the%20perpetrators%20residing%20in%20that%20village%20in%20Nalbari%20district%20for%20some%20time%20to%20target%20the%20victim%20%E2%80%93%20she%20was%20Haloi%E2%80%99s%20second%20wife%2C%20and%20that%20information%20might%20have%20been%20key%3B%20she%20was%20no%20%E2%80%98Sati%20Savitri%E2%80%99%20after%20all.%20Only%20%E2%80%98Sati%20Savitris%2C%E2%80%99%20as%20per%20an%20Indian%20male-controlled%20society%2C%20have%20a%20right%20to%20dignity%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fkuki-woman-from-viral-video-speaks-out-on-sexual-assault-witnessing-murders%5C%22%3EKuki%20Woman%20From%20Viral%20Video%20Speaks%20Out%20on%20Sexual%20Assault%2C%20Witnessing%20Murders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevenge%2C%20retribution%20and%20a%20vicious%20cycle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%20on%20May%204%2C%20as%20per%20the%20testimonials%20of%20the%20survivors%2C%20the%20Meitei%20men%20told%20them%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Eour%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewomen%20were%20raped%20by%20%3Cem%3Eyour%3C%2Fem%3E%20men%20in%20Churachandpur%20(that%20contention%20was%20based%20on%20a%20fake%20video).%20Therefore%2C%20their%20women%20were%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20through%20their%20bodies.%20Case%20after%20case%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20in%20conflict%20zones%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20state%20immunity%20have%20also%20held%20up%20that%20the%20same%20rule%20could%20be%20operative%20%E2%80%93%20their%20women%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20price%20with%20their%20bodies%20for%20their%20men%E2%80%99s%20fault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20after%20that%20wretched%20Nalbari%20case%2C%20on%20another%20humid%20summer%20day%2C%20in%20neighbouring%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20also%20under%20AFSPA%20then%20%E2%80%93%20Thangjam%20Manorama%20was%20allegedly%20raped%2C%20brutally%20tortured%20and%20killed%20by%20an%20Assam%20Rifles%20team.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20allow%20ourselves%20here%20to%20ignore%20the%20thought%20that%20Manorama%20went%20through%20what%20she%20did%20also%20because%20she%20was%20being%20made%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20as%20%3Cem%3Etheir%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20also%20reckon%20here%20that%20the%20horrifying%20Manorama%20case%20from%20July%202004%20gave%20independent%20India%20the%20most%20powerful%2C%20and%20distressing%2C%20symbol%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20resistance%20to%20state-sponsored%20rape%20%E2%80%93%20around%2030%20middle-aged%20Meitei%20women%20who%20belonged%20to%20Manorama%E2%80%99s%20community%20stripped%20naked%20in%20front%20of%20the%20citadel%20of%20their%20honour%2C%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20standing%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20to%20protest%20the%20sexual%20abuse.%20That%20incident%20made%20the%20country%20note%20with%20shock%20and%20horror%20what%20was%20happening%20to%20women%20in%20Manipur%20then%20%E2%80%93%20only%20to%20be%20replaced%20on%20another%20July%20day%2C%20nearly%2020%20years%20later%2C%20by%20yet%20another%20horrifying%20sight%20of%20what%20a%20set%20of%20women%20from%20that%20state%20had%20to%20undergo%20during%20another%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwomen-of-the-northeast-present-a-picture-of-contrasts%5C%22%3EWomen%20of%20the%20Northeast%20Present%20a%20Picture%20of%20Contrasts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20speaks.%20And%20he%20does%20not.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20perpetrators%20were%20Meitei%20men.%20The%20gaze%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20in%20both%20the%20crimes%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20acknowledge%2C%20has%20not%20altered%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Manorama%20was%20seen%20as%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20woman%20by%20her%20perpetrators%2C%20the%20Kuki%20women%20were%20also%20looked%20at%20as%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%20by%20the%20Meitei%20mob.%20It%20gave%20both%20sets%20of%20culprits%20the%20license%20to%20sexually%20assault%20a%20woman%20during%20a%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20May%204%20video%20kicking%20up%20nationwide%20outrage%2C%20finally%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fseventy-nine-days-after-violence-broke-out-narendra-modi-finally-talks-about-manipur%5C%22%3Ewas%20forced%20to%20break%20his%20silence%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Manipur.%20That%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20about%20those%20survivors%20inside%20the%20temple%20of%20our%20democracy%2C%20the%20Parliament%2C%20as%20the%20norm%20is%2C%20but%20outside%20it%2C%20and%20also%20not%20without%20attacking%20opposition-ruled%20states%2C%20may%20be%20overlooked%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20focusing%20on%20what%20he%20said.%20After%20all%2C%20absorbing%20the%20string%20of%20sentences%20%E2%80%93%20spoken%20post%20a%20deathly%2C%20unprecedented%20silence%20over%20nearly%20three%20months%20%E2%80%93%20must%20take%20precedence%20over%20propriety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20too%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20male-controlled%20gaze%20of%20%3Cem%3Eour%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%20could%20be%20spotted.%20Modi%20rightly%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Csorrow%20and%20anger%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20incident%3B%20he%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20shameful%20act%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20most%20operational%20part%20of%20that%20short%20speech%20spoken%20in%20front%20of%20a%20battery%20of%20TV%20cameras%20was%20this%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20daughters%20of%20Manipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanipur-sc-steps-in-pm-breaks-silence-opp-wants-his-statement-in-parliament-8851376%2F%5C%22%3Ecan%20never%20be%20forgiven%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20he%20expressed%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20over%20the%20survivors%20%E2%80%93%20as%20%3Cem%3Eour%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%2C%20%3Cem%3Eour%20%3C%2Fem%3Edaughters%20whose%20perpetrators%20must%20be%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Talked%20About%20the%20Manipur%20Violence.%20But%20Did%20He%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBilkis%20Bano%20redux%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20nine%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbilkis-bano-husband-convict-release%5C%22%3Eokayed%20the%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20as%20many%20as%2011%20convicted%20rapists%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%20of%20Gujarat.%20When%20you%20juxtapose%20his%20July%2020%20speech%20against%20that%20October%202022%20decision%2C%20you%20are%20left%20wondering%2C%20what%20must%20be%20the%20reason%20for%20Modi%20choosing%20to%20be%20the%20first%20Indian%20prime%20minster%20to%20support%20a%20set%20of%20convicted%20rapists%20being%20released%20from%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20woman%20at%20play%20then%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20Bilki