3EKMB%E2%80%99s%20public%20commentary%20to%20non-dissenting%20shareholders%20paints%20a%20picture%20of%20employee%20contentment%20and%20loyalty%20to%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20speaks%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9CDrona%E2%80%9D%20programme%2C%20which%20is%20aimed%20at%20training%20youngsters%20for%20long-term%20careers%20in%20the%20bank.%20%E2%80%98Drona%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cflagship%20managerial%20capability%20development%20programme%E2%80%9D%20aimed%20at%20assessing%20a%20manager%20as%20a%20trainer%2C%20mentor%2C%20and%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20these%20efforts%2C%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20attrition%20rate%20is%20even%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20other%20banks%20like%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20Yes%20Bank%2C%20and%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India.%20And%20the%20high%20attrition%20rate%20impacts%20KMB%20more%20than%20the%20other%20banks%20as%20a%20large%20proportion%20of%20the%20new%20hires%20are%20in%20the%20under-30%20years%20category.%20Eighty-four%20percent%20of%20them%20are%20new%20recruits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21145754%2Fimage-1152.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21145754%2Fimage-1152.png%201172w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21145754%2Fimage-1152-300x92.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21145754%2Fimage-1152-1024x315.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22361%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENote%3A%20The%20FY23%20annual%20reports%20of%20HDFC%20Bank%20and%20ICICI%20Bank%20have%20not%20been%20released%20yet%20till%20the%20ti