0both%20banks%2C%20stakeholders%20can%20only%20conclude%20that%20these%20workplaces%20are%20not%20providing%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20female%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20strikingly%20high%20attrition%20rates%2C%20one%20would%20expect%20the%20directors%20and%20executive%20management%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20problem%20and%20engage%20in%20a%20thorough%20discussion%20of%20its%20causes%20and%20potential%20remedial%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegrettably%2C%20as%20with%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20FY23%20annual%20report%20lacks%20an%20in-depth%20analysis%20of%20the%20issue%20beyond%20mandatory%20attrition%20disclosure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20however%2C%20KMB%20does%20provide%20a%20voluntary%20disclosure%20on%20attrition%20data%20in%20various%20other%20sub-segments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20claim%20of%20adhering%20to%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20corporate%20governance%2C%20which%20includes%20disclosure%2C%20transparency%2C%20and%20responsiveness%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20commentary%20on%20this%20critical%20issue%20raises%20doubts%20about%20the%20genuineness%20of%20their%20commitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20further%20insights%2C%20this%20analyst%20sent%20the%20bank%20specific%20queries%20pertaining%20to%20attrition%2C%20its%20likely%20causes%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20commentary%20by%20the%20board%2C%20but%20the%20bank%2C%20just%20like%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20has%20declined%20to%20respond%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20attrition%20issue%20in%20private%20sector%20banks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20significant%20attrition%20problem%20within%20the%20private%20sector%20banking%20industry%2C%20and%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fmarket%2Fstock-market-news%2Ffrom-hdfc-bank-to-sbi-here-are-indias-top-10-biggest-banks-check-here-11688177693624.html%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20lar