her%20concrete%20constructions%20have%20damaged%20the%20sensitive%20ecology%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20DUSIB%20Act%2C%20the%20government%20can%20only%20demolish%20already%20existing%20unauthorised%20%3Cem%3Ejhuggi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ejhopadis%3C%2Fem%3E%20only%20after%20providing%20rehabilitation%20for%20the%20people%20staying%20there.%20But%20in%20case%20of%20Bela%20estate%2C%20no%20rehabilitation%20was%20done%2C%20which%20left%20people%20who%20had%20already%20been%20displaced%20as%20part%20of%20G20%20beautification%20drives%2C%20with%20no%20homes%20during%20the%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F1JyOLHiYusE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689938986000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21165322%2F00143.00_02_13_25.Still004.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fwatch-delhi-floofs-g20-eviction-homeless%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20problems%20of%20the%20already%20homeless%20people%20of%20Delhi's%20Bela%20estate%20have%20doubled%20after%20the%20recent%20flooding%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fwatch-delhi-floofs-g20-eviction-homeless%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20'Video%20Tarnished%20State's%20Image%2C'%20Says%20CM%20Biren%2C%20Calls%20for%20Statewide%20Protests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20day%20after%20a%20harrowing%20video%20showing%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20men%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Thoumbal%20district%20garnered%20outrage%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20said%20that%20he%20has%20called%20for%20statewide%20protests%20in%20condemnation%20over%20the%20video%20that%20has%20%E2%80%9Ctarnished%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20image.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStatewide%2C%20the%20video%20which%20became%20viral%E2%80%A6we%20need%20to%20condemn%20it%20statewide.%20Because%20this%20state%20that%20we%20have%2C%20the%20people%20who%20live%20in%20it%2C%20they%20consider%20women%20their%20mothers.%20But%20miscreants%20did%20this%20and%20tarnished%20our%20image.%20So%20this%20is%20why%2C%20statewide%2C%20all%20over%20the%20state%2C%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20in%20the%20valleys%2C%20wherever%2C%20we%20will%20condemn%20this.%20The%20ones%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20crime%20will%20be%20given%20the%20harshest%20of%20punishments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20PTI%2C%20in%20mix%20of%20Hindi%20and%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiren%20has%20been%20facing%20intense%20criticism%20over%20his%20administration%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20handle%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203.%20Many%20quarters%20have%20blamed%20him%20for%20fomenting%20the%20violence%20or%20supporting%20one%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20further%20criticised%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20only%20after%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20that%20the%20first%20arrest%20was%20made%20in%20the%20case%2C%2078%20days%20after%20the%20crime%20took%20place.%20This%20arrest%20was%20announced%20by%20Biren%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMy%20hearts%20go%20out%20to%20the%20two%20women%20who%20were%20subjected%20to%20a%20deeply%20disrespectful%20and%20inh