0the%20offensive%20against%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20statement%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20his%20social%20media%20army%20began%20attacking%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20questioning%20why%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20speaking%20out%20against%20violence%20towards%20women%20in%20Congress-ruled%20states.%20This%2C%20when%20the%20world%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20images%20of%20mass%20brutality%20that%20the%20Kuki%20women%20were%20subjected%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20nearly%20three%20months%20of%20majoritarian%20violence%20faced%20by%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kuki%20people%20was%20overshadowed%20and%20reduced%20to%20a%20matter%20of%20violence%20against%20women.%20Such%20violence%20is%20an%20everyday%20reality%20for%20women%20across%20all%20states%20in%20India%20and%20even%20globally%2C%20often%20in%20the%20most%20horrifying%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20surfaced%20showing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3Etwo%20Kuki%20women%20stripped%20naked%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20paraded%20them%2C%20nearly%20three%20months%20after%20the%20incident.%20The%20FIR%20states%20there%20were%20three%20women%20survivors%20of%20the%20incident.%20This%20video%20horrified%20people%2C%20and%20public%20reactions%20of%20disbelief%20and%20outrage%20were%20evident.%20However%2C%20can%20the%20same%20be%20said%20about%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20country%3F%20Or%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%3F%20Not%20to%20mention%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20who%20spent%20three%20days%20in%20Manipur%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20elections.%20Are%20we%20expected%20to%20believe%20that%20they%2C%20like%20ordinary%20people%2C%20only%20learned%20about%20this%20incident%20through%20the%20video%20and%20were%20unaware%20of%20the%20violence%20inflicted%20upon%20the%20Kuki%20people%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Talked%20About%20the%20Manipur%20Violence.%20But%20Did%20He%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20were%20the%20case%2C%20we%20should%20question%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20they%20were%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20complaints%20filed%20by%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20violated%20women%20with%20the%20police%20and%20the%20National%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Commission.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20actively%20provoked%20majoritarian%20violence%20against%20Kukis%2C%20received%20support%20from%20violent%20Meitei%20groups%2C%20a%20well-known%20fact%2C%20and%20let%20it%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20speech%2C%20Modi%20cheerfully%20talked%20about%20the%20month%20of%20%3Cem%3Esawan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(monsoon)%20and%20the%20youth%E2%80%99s%20connection%20with%20digital%20India%2C%20before%20briefly%20touching%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20showing%20his%20indifference%20to%20the%20issue%20that%20deeply%20affects%20the%20nation%20and%20utter%20disdain%20for%20it.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20reveals%20his%20smugness%20and%20confidence%20that%20he%20has%20debased%20the%20sensibilities%20of%20his%20constituents%2C%20making%20them%20accept%20his%20cunning%20and%20vileness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20sexual%20assault%20and%20murders%20are%20forms%20of%20violence%2C%20the%20violence%20perpetrated%20against%20an%20entire%20community%20due%20to%20their%20identity%20falls%20into%20a%20different%2C%20more%20severe%20category.%20The%20women%20violated%20in%20Manipur%20were%20Kuki%2C%20and%20the%20attackers%20belonged%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20The%20sexual%20assault%20was%20part%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20violence%20instigated%20by%20the%20Meitei%20groups%20with%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20tacit%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20incorrect%20to%20claim%20that%20fake%20news%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20Meitei%20woman%20incited%20the%20Meitei%20people%20to%20seek%20revenge%20by%20attacking%20these%20women.%20It%20is%20more%20likely%20that%20the%20fake%20news%20aimed%20to%20provide%20cover%20for%20the%20sexual%20violence%20inflicted%20upon%20the%20Kuki%20women%20and%20find%20an%20excuse%20for%20it.%20Hence%2C%20those%20who%20spread%20the%20fake%20news%20and%20attacked%20the%20Kuki%20women%20were%20the%20same%20%E2%80%93%20violent%20Meitei%20groups%20who%20also%20mobilised%20common%20Meitei%20individuals%20to%20partake%20in%20violence%20against%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanipur-sexual-assault-mob-video-women-police-8849995%2F%5C%22%3Enot%20just%20the%20mob%20perpetrating%20the%20violence%2C%20but%20the%20state%20police%20also%20participated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20handing%20over%20the%20women%20to%20the%20mob.%20They%20were%20not%20forcibly%20snatched%20by%20the%20mob%20as%20some%20may%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20wrong%20and%20perhaps%20naive%20of%20us%20to%20expect%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20speak%20out%20as%20he%20is%20part%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20and%20his%20brand%20of%20politics%20is%20responsible%20for%20it.%20Modi%20was%20in%20a%20similar%20position%20as%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20now%2C%20when%20he%20presided%20over%20a%20pogrom%20against%20Muslims%20in%20Gujarat%20two%20decades%20ago%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20a%20master%20of%20denial%2C%20but%20more%20alarmingly%2C%20he%20mobilises%20and%20leads%20a%20violent%20mob%2C%20attacking%20those%20who%20seek%20justice.%20His%20continuation%20in%20power%20will%20mean%20the%20death%20of%20everything%20that%20makes%20a%20people%20truly%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor